# Submission Intake, OCR, and Privacy

- Digital input may be pasted text or TXT, DOCX, PDF, HTML/HTM, and Markdown.
- Reuse document parsing without calling RAG upload, chunking, embedding, retrieval, or Qdrant.
- Scanned PDF/JPEG/PNG OCR is a draft transcript; feedback is blocked until staff verification.
- Prefer Canvas source references over copying binaries. Use the restricted writing GridFS bucket only when review requires a retained staff upload.
- Key records by internal IDs and Canvas IDs only where necessary; never store PUID.
- Retention must be configurable and production-approved. No silent permanent storage.
- Errors and logs may include internal record IDs/statuses, never submission text or OAuth secrets.
